{
  "texts": [
    "Nevertheless, in contrast to the outcomes reported in [10, 13], both GPT-4 and GPT-3.5-turbo achieved high accuracy in their responses.",
    "This result might be due to the relative simplicity of the false-belief tasks.",
    "Similarly to the observations made by [14], we identified a certain degree of hyper-accuracy in GPT-4 in comparison to the preceding model, GPT-3.5-turbo.",
    "This distinction was particularly prominent in the change of location task.",
    "While GPT-3.5-turbo conformed to the pattern of progressively improving accuracy with increasing age, GPT-4 exhibited a high proportion of correct answers even when simulating 1-year-olds."
  ]
}